title: Oregon high school senior takes viral yearbook photos at 7-Eleven
text:
On October 11th, Hermiston high school senior, Stefano Peiris, Tweeted that he took his yearbook portraits at 7-Eleven.
The internet went wild.
Since then, his Tweet received over 35,000 likes and 57,000 favorites. National media sites like Seventeen , MTV News and Elite Daily posted about the Oregon teen's unique photoshoot.
Watch the video to find out why he chose 7-Eleven and the message he's trying to spread.
